Package ure.terrain

Class TerrainI

  • java.lang.Object
    • ure.terrain.TerrainI
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, UTerrain, UAnimator
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Blank, Door, Lava, Pit, Stairs, Water
    public abstract class TerrainI
extends java.lang.Object
implements UTerrain, java.lang.Cloneable, UAnimator
    A real serializable instance of a terrain which exists in a single cell. Subclass this to create new subtypes of Terrain. To extend base terrain, use TerrainDeco. For API reference when extending this class to create custom terrain types, see the method docs of TerrainDeco.
